&gt; After some cycles of flight, he figured he was near the spark&#39;s
&gt; position. He transformed to dragon mode and a cloud of frost shot out
&gt; from his armor plates. He looked around, but saw no one.
&gt; 
&gt; AzureBlade: Hello? Is there anyone here?
&gt; 
&gt; 

Hearing a voice, it sounded like something from a human fantasy fairy or some 
strange special effect to her. Her audion receptors were clouded by the 
strange energetic waters. Her optics tried to locate the voice. 

But, with a step from the waterfall, it seemed as though she were like some 
spirit that just appeared from the water, her form shimmering from the energy 
water & the sun. Her crimson optics glowed as she caught the sight of the blue 
dragon before her on the edge of the lagoon. She stood there, just... watching 
him. Cocking her head to the side. She seemed... innocent at the moment. 
But... lost. 

Standing on the stones a moment, her feathery mane whipped around her by the 
turbulence in the air caused by the waterfall & wind. her wings were heavily 
damaged, but her form seemed to be healing. A gift from the waters of this 
strange lagoon. 

Her crimson optics gazed at the blue dragon as she stood there as though she 
were standing on the water itself. Her form still shimmering. 


